OL,3,CEx-police officer, 29, denies
OL,4,C'intimate relationships' with four
OL,5,Ccriminals
OL,7,FA former police officer has denied
OL,8,Fhaving intimate relationships with
OL,9,Ffour criminals and accessing
OL,10,Finformation about them on the police
OL,11,Fdatabase.
OL,13,FKayleigh Moye, 29, who worked for West
OL,14,FMidlands Police, pleaded not guilty to
OL,15,Ffour charges of misconduct relating to
OL,16,Ffour individuals, allegedly committed
OL,17,Fbetween September 2022 and December
OL,18,F2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
