OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773072685
OL,3,CEx-police officer, 29, denies
OL,4,C'intimate relationships' with four
OL,5,Ccriminals
OL,7,FMoye, who is on unconditional bail,
OL,8,Fappeared at Birmingham Crown Court
OL,9,Ftoday on Monday 9 March.
OL,11,FBirmingham Crown Court heard Moye, of
OL,12,FQuinton in Birmingham, allegedly
OL,13,Faccessed confidential information
OL,14,Fabout four people on West Midlands
OL,15,FPolice computer systems, who the
OL,16,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,17,Fpreviously said were criminals, and
OL,18,Ffailed to notify police of her
OL,19,Frelationships with each of them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
