OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773072685
OL,3,CEx-police officer, 29, denies
OL,4,C'intimate relationships' with four
OL,5,Ccriminals
OL,7,FShe also pleaded not guilty to three
OL,8,Fdrugs charges - one of being concerned
OL,9,Fin the supply of a cannabis on 20
OL,10,FNovember 2023, and two of possessing
OL,11,Fcannabis on dates in December 2023 and
OL,12,FFebruary 2024.
OL,14,FMoye was told she will face a trial in
OL,15,FSeptember 2028.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
